@NODE goldkeys "Gold keys"

These keys are used to free Merry-Men. The Bungee Key can be collected
without hitting Fire button in joystick.

Properties:

Key ID - the identify number of this key. Use values 1-8 for gold keys.
@ENDNODE
@NODE silverkeys "Silver keys"

These keys are used to open doors/gates. The Ghost Key will appear for
a limited amount of time once the specific property of the other object
changes.

Properties:

Key ID - the identify number of this key. Use values 11-15 for silver keys.

Properties for Ghost Key:

Time - the amount of time in seconds for the key to appear
Appear - this is an unhandled property type in version v2.0. In future
         version it will describe the activation property of the key.
@ENDNODE
@NODE boots "Boots"

These are items that once picked up will be worn by a hero.

The Gummy Boots allows for longer jumps.
The Snow Boots allows to walk on ice.
The Gravity Boots allows to walk in zero-gravity area.

